dialogs.dialog_info_message_description_160:
&lt;p&gt;Tomorrow we will be offering you the chance to test our new event: BEYOND THE HORIZON&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://imgur.com/5fgXoJH.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;100&amp;percnt;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will be a &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;test&lt;/span&gt; and as such there might be some bugs that we need to iron out still. However we do hope that you will test this event for us and help us improve the event for the future. To that end we would like to let you know a few details about how the event works.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need to be level 30 and a member of an Alliance before the event starts if you want to take part.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When you start you will be assigned to a new Alliance composed of the other members from your main account Alliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;These new Alliances are restricted to twenty members and the first to join will be the Leader.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will need to attack City States on the map to gain Influence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This Influence is what your alliance needs to win the event.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Every day the Influence you have gained will be transferred to the vaults in the Alliance Capital.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rivals will be able to attack you or the Alliance Capital to steal a portion of the accumulated Influence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You and your Alliance members will have to focus on both attack and defence and only by organising well will you be able to compete and win this event.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We hope you enjoy our new event!&lt;/p&gt;

